Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:04.52,Saku-main,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next up is the weather forecast \Nfor the Kanto Region.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:07.28,Saku-main,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Due to areas of low pressure \Ncoming in from the west,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:10.47,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}some areas may experience \Nrain this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:08.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:11.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:14.07,Saku-main,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If you plan to go out, take \Nan umbrella with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.46,0:00:18.03,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you leaving Sakura Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:29.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like, if I stay in Sakura Hall, \NI'll start to hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:31.98,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hate yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm leaving Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:40.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to leave from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:46.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the deadline for the \NNew Artist Award coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:48.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:51.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Until I leave Sakura Hall, \NI'll still look after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:00:58.95,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:04.84,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina has been working \Nthrough the night, every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:07.66,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing and redrawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:09.96,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,drawing and redrawing \Nover and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.37,0:01:14.16,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,On the morning of the deadline for\N entries to the New Artist Award,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:17.47,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,she finally finished her manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:21.43,Sign,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,After you eat, get some rest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:26.24,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The only cats who still need \Nowners are Nozomi and Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:37.36,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Goal: Escape from Sakura Hall!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:29.05,Saku-main,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Unfortunately, the Milky Way \Nwill not be visible tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:34.23,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally taken the \Nfirst step toward moving back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:35.90,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,into the regular dorms...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.28,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:48.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:52.94,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:53.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:55.49,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.26,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:58.26,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:00.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:05.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:06.94,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:10.90,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted you to tell her how \Ncute she was, how you couldn't bear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:13.48,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and how you wanted to play \N"naughty administrator" with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Some of that is definitely sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:16.86,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:19.29,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She said we're celebrating Tanabata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:21.66,Sign,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}For Kouhai-kun: Make a wish upon \Nthe night sky. What is your wish!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.66,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki gave me one for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:24.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.25,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall Tanabata Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.96,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:04.34,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of kids, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:08.14,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kids tend to flock to Kamiigusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.71,Saku-overlap,KIDS,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.14,Saku-overlap,KIDS,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:11.00,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because her \Nmental age is close to theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.13,Saku-main,KIDS,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, I want to hang one up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.02,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll lift you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:15.94,Saku-main,KID,0000,0000,0000,,Higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Higher, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:18.35,Saku-main,KID,0000,0000,0000,,A little higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:21.15,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you touch her, you'll be crossing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.53,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,the River Styx instead of the Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.66,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin! Come write something, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:26.50,Saku-main,KID,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hang mine over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.22,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.75,Sign,WISH,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could fire laser beams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.95,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's not signed, \Nit's obvious who wrote this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:38.87,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.72,Saku-main,KID,0000,0000,0000,,A little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.75,Saku-main,KID,0000,0000,0000,,A little higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.66,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't Tanabata anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.07,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.07,Saku-overlap,KID,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.14,Sign,WISH,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he would look at me someday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:56.06,Sign,WISH,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he would look at me someday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.77,Saku-main,MIASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.67,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you wish you'll \Nwin the New Artist Award?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.49,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's amazing about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:19.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're just brilliant, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:22.55,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The clouds are still in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.05,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Still?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.65,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go hang this on the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hang one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.61,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:56.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I should've wished it wouldn't rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.44,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give this to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:06.14,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now Orihime won't \Nget to see Hikoboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.96,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll live happily ever after!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:11.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you take a bath later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.81,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call: Iida Ayano
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.94,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.86,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mashiron...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.91,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,She's not wearing that necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:30.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But that wasn't a date, \Nit was a misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.13,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:42.61,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't selected for \Nthe New Artist Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll do better next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to dwell \Non the New Artist Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.03,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you've got \Nan editor, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.30,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:07.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're on a whole different \Nlevel from those others guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:11.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's no big deal if you \Ndon't win the New Artist—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.89,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.06,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.77,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.19,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.57,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.16,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that Misaki's new anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,had its public debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her new anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That thing she showed us at \NShiina's welcoming party?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.28,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's been well-received.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.44,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Made it to a million hits in just three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:11.31,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She's already received ten offers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.18,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to commercialize her five-minute anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:20.31,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was looking forward \Nto Misaki's new work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:23.77,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:27.54,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only person who \Nwanted her to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:32.32,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted her \Nto crash and burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You must see right through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:44.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually a little relieved \NShiina wasn't selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:51.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina worked so hard to \Nwin the New Artist Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.01,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The thing about talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:02.17,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is that it unconsciously \Nwraps up and destroys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.73,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:08.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The closer you are to it, \Nthe more it tears you to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.33,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who live \Nin a place that ordinary men...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.40,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,can never reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:19.07,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's a world above the clouds \N that we can't even see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:26.07,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of world they live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:33.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Misaki-senpai \Ncares about talent or ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.99,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:42.35,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know how to \Naccept the difference...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,between Misaki and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.90,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day I can proudly \Nstand by her side,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,all I can do is struggle in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:55.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san, do you like Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.87,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go get some ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.33,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:05.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Shiina will be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:10.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It might be weird for me to \Nworry about her now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:14.10,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with feeling both ways, \Nif it's how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.79,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Things like this are never simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.26,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall Tanabata Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.22,Sign,BOOKS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4}An Introduction to Programming\NProgramming Practice\NSkills Necessary for Programming Games
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:21.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.77,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I don't need those books anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.52,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I don't need those books anymore.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: But why did you give them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.90,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I don't need those books anymore.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: But why did you give them to me?\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Because I thought you\N needed them. They're a parting gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,He stays cooped up in his room,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.20,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but he knows how to read a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.66,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I don't need those books anymore.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: But why did you give them to me?\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Because I thought you\N needed them. They're a parting gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.66,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I don't need those books anymore.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: But why did you give them to me?\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Because I thought you\N needed them. They're a parting gift.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Akasaka, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.79,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: But why did you give them to me?\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Because I thought you\N needed them. They're a parting gift.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Akasaka, I have a question.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.04,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Because I thought you\N needed them. They're a parting gift.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Akasaka, I have a question.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: What?\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Do you think getting close \Nto prodigious talent will destroy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.59,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Akasaka, I have a question.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: What?\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Do you think getting close \Nto prodigious talent will destroy me?\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I don't know what \Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.03,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: What?\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Do you think getting close \Nto prodigious talent will destroy me?\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I don't know what \Nyou're talking about.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: But, at the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.93,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:07.30,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about being destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.95,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,until you've read those books so \Nthoroughly, you feel like you're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:14.19,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Sincerely, someone who prefers \NSenpachi to Kinpachi: Maid-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Until I feel like I'm done for, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.01,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:48.43,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Please Knock\NMashiron's Room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave your breakfast here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever cleans this stuff up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:11.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are they going to do when I'm gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.96,Sign,WISH,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could fire laser beams
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:20.30,Sign,WISH,0000,0000,0000,,I wish for Sorata's wish to come true
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:20.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.53,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Haven't you heard the expression:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Let your face smile, \Nlet your heart cry"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What does she mean by my "wish"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:31.58,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.21,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Taken literally, it's \N a nice, positive phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.98,Sign,PAPER,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}Career Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.65,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But the truth is, it secretly \Nhides a great sadness inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.28,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I took the day off work—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I mean, I've got the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:51.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look for someone \Nto take the cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:55.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:03.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Once Nozomi and Hikari are \Ngone, you can finally move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.81,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:24.78,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just by looking at you, \NI can sort of tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.79,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:34.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.00,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.06,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Crazy way to hit on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:37.88,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Stolen love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.07,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.38,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Poor Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.77,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I like sweet things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.53,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I like the union of sweet and salty flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.60,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,How is Shiina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.46,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nanohana Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:10.67,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san's art is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:13.04,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Her only weakness is her stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.89,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,So I told her to use \Nevents actually occurring...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,at Sakura Hall as reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina and my roles are reversed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.50,Saku-overlap,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.49,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,The boy who couldn't even choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.91,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,his own underwear \Nactually had a clear goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.13,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, the heroine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.06,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,can't find anything she wants to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:43.02,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, some stuff happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.78,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.69,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:58.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,this powerfully abrupt \Nending isn't a happy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:03.25,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,This is the main reason Shiina-san \Nfailed to win the award.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:07.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The heroine is leaving Nanohana Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:11.76,Sign,MANGA,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:11.76,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I told her over and \Nover again to fix the ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:15.63,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,But she wouldn't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:16.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:22.17,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,She said it was your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.43,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,An ending that captures the \Ncareening drive of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.61,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,It's sending shivers down my spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:36.10,Saku-thought,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,This might work...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.75,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:44.82,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.38,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanda? \NDid you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:49.10,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:54.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I have to start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:55.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.69,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:07.57,Sign,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,Career Plan\NSuimei University of the Arts: Media Studies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.11,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.36,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:16.33,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san, is this what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.28,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:23.17,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,You should write the ending you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.93,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The ending I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.21,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.88,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,What's the ending you want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:36.03,Sign,MANGA,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.85,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:45.10,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My wish isn't to leave Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.48,Sign,BOOK,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming a Programmer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:53.68,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was putting pressure on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:58.80,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was just running from Sakura \NHall... from reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.20,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:14.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:20.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay there. Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:23.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:27.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I submitted my career plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:31.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go into Media \NStudies and make video games!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even thinking about participating \Nin a development audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.79,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:35.53,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a game designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:43.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been interested, \Nbut I was too scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I kept thinking about what \Nwould happen if I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I kept lining up reasons not to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:55.38,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,like "it's a waste of time," \Nor "I'll just get my feelings hurt,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.67,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and gave up on it altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:03.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But watching you made \Nme want to try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:09.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'll be like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You were up drawing all night again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:56.90,Sign,MANGA,0000,0000,0000,,I... I want to stay at Nanohana Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:56.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay at Nanohana Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:04.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is the happy ending \Nyou really wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is this doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:18.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:19.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:23.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:28.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Shiina's cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, thanks for earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina. Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:42.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.54,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Your debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:52.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, you idiot. Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't win the New Artist Award...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:58.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,but if you fix up your manuscript,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll print it in next month's issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:04.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've already \Nfixed them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:13.89,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I should be happy, but I'm crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:17.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:25.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to celebrate your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.08,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Call me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.35,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Not that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No, I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've never called a girl by her first name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:53.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You call Misaki by her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:54.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:55.85,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,And Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's an Amazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:59.11,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.22,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You knew what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:13.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.42,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.90,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're naive, Sorata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:25.00,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's youth for you! \NIt makes your heart race!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.82,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sweating over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:29.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, how long were you guys listening in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:31.71,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:32.27,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Gasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:36.06,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! What is it? Tell me, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.63,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something you \Nwant to tell us, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on. Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:45.16,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Show us how you really feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for causing such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:56.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:59.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stay at Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:05.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron, congratulations \Non your debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:09.06,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,And kouhai-kun, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.64,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:16.06,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended it was someone else's \Nfault that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.80,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:24.68,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you put your mind to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:27.28,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,you can change the color of \Nyour world in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:31.78,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall is a haphazard \Nmix of all different colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:37.87,Sign,WISH,0000,0000,0000,,I wish for Sorata's wish to come true
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:40.34,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably never change...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:49.89,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1272,1)}#04 A World of Changing Colors
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:34.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari is female.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:41.06,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(489,1)}#05 The Serious Girl of Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:39.59,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari says she has a hunch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.59,0:23:41.06,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll soon be more females.
